Hadoop
Java based framework which supports storage and processing of a huge data set.

Components of Hadoop Framework
HDFS- Big data storage layer
      1- NameNode(Master node)
      2-DataNode(slave node)
MapReduce - data processing in parallel(schedules jobs, monitoring and re-executing)
      1-JobTracker
      2-TaskTracker

Reasons to learn Big Data Technologies
-Errors within the organizantion are known instantly
-Strategies of competitors are known immediately
-Improved service
-Cost savings
-Keep up with the consumer trends
